---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout minimal title="Privacy — danctrl.dev" description="Privacy policy for danctrl.dev — what data is collected and how it's handled.">
  <section class="flex min-h-screen items-start justify-center px-6 pt-16 pb-24">
    <div class="w-full max-w-2xl">
      <!-- Back to Home button -->
      <a
        href="/"
        class="btn-secondary mb-8 inline-flex h-[44px] items-center gap-2 rounded-lg px-5 text-sm font-semibold"
      >
        <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 17l-4-4m0 0l4-4m-4 4h18" />
        </svg>
        Back to Home
      </a>

      <div class="section-card section-card--static rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-12">
        <h1 class="mb-8 font-mono text-xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] sm:text-2xl dark:text-white">Privacy Policy</h1>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
          <p>
            This is the personal portfolio of <strong class="text-[#1a1a1a] dark:text-white">Daniel Guntermann</strong>. This site does not collect personal data beyond what is technically necessary.
          </p>

          <div>
            <h2 class="mb-2 font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-[#1a1a1a] dark:text-white">Third-party services</h2>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li><strong class="text-[#1a1a1a] dark:text-white">Cloudflare Analytics</strong> &mdash; cookie-free, privacy-friendly analytics. No personal data stored.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-[#1a1a1a] dark:text-white">Cloudflare Turnstile</strong> &mdash; bot protection on the contact form. No tracking cookies.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-[#1a1a1a] dark:text-white">Fonts</strong> &mdash; JetBrains Mono and Poppins are self-hosted on this site. No requests are made to Google Fonts or any external font CDN.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="mb-2 font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-[#1a1a1a] dark:text-white">Contact form</h2>
            <p>Data submitted via the contact form (name, email, message) is only used to respond to your enquiry and not stored beyond that.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="mb-2 font-mono text-sm font-semibold text-[#1a1a1a] dark:text-white">Local storage</h2>
            <p>A single <code class="rounded bg-gray-100 px-1 dark:bg-white/10">theme</code> key is stored in <code class="rounded bg-gray-100 px-1 dark:bg-white/10">localStorage</code> to remember your light/dark mode preference. No tracking cookies are used.</p>
          </div>

          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-600">Last updated: February 2026</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
